**Edit:**  

In case anyone was wondering, the `@import` approach causes the same undesired behaviour, ie:

```
@import url(&#39;https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans|Roboto+Mono|Work+Sans:400,700&amp;display=swap&#39;);
```


